y</span> 2010</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Resolution+adopted+by+the+General+Assembly%3A++55%2F2.+United+Nations+Millennium+Declaration&amp;rft.pub=United+Nations&amp;rft.date=2000-09-06%2F2000-09-08&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fmillennium%2Fdeclaration%2Fares552e.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASafe+household+water+storage\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-UN_Prog_Rpt-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-UN_Prog_Rpt_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><sup class=\"reference\" style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">:<span> 48</span></sup>\n<cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.un.org/millenniumgoals/pdf/MDG_Report_2009_ENG.pdf\">\"The Millennium Development Goals Report\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. United Nations. 2009<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">3 February</span> 2010</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+Millennium+Development+Goals+Report&amp;rft.pub=United+Nations&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fmillenniumgoals%2Fpdf%2FMDG_Report_2009_ENG.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASafe+household+water+storage\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">\n<cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.who.int/household_water/en/\">\"Household Water Treatment and Safe Storage\"</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/World_Health_Organization\" title=\"World Health Organization\">World Health Organization</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">3 February</span> 2010</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Household+Water+Treatment+and+Safe+Storage&amp;rft.pub=World+Health+Organization&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fhousehold_water%2Fen%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASafe+household+water+storage\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Safe_household_water_storage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>World Health Organization (WHO): <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.who.int/household_water/en/\">Household Water Treatment and Safe Storage (HWTS) program.</a></li>\n<li>Plasticology 101 (CPS) <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.containerandpackaging.com/info/plasticology.asp\">Clear real world explanations about household water storage.</a></li>\n<li>WHO/SDE/WSH/02.07 report:  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.who.int/water_sanitation_health/dwq/wsh0207/en/index.html\"><i>Managing water in the home: accelerated health gains from improved water supply</i></a>  prepared by Professor Mark D. Sobsey, School of Public Health, University of North Carolina, Chapel Hill, North Carolina, USA, report covers many aspects of a HWTS system including storage, treatment, social/economic aspects, and monitoring.\n<ul><li>Portion of above report most pertinent to this article is <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.who.int/water_sanitation_health/dwq/wsh0207/en/index3.html\"